title: U R Mala Kuhinja
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Organic, Take-out, Asian, Fusion, BYOB, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Asian fusion cuisine restaurant, moved to this larger location in 2014 from Josipa Stadlera BR6. Free Wi-Fi. Specify to your server if you are veg/vegan, and the kitchen will accommodate. In 2014 relocated 100m east of previous location.
